<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.5">
<l>puṭṭiyiṟ cēṟum puḻutiyum koṇṭuvantu</l>
<l>vaṭṭi yamukki yakampuk kaṟiyāmē</l>
<l>caṭṭit tayirum taṭāviṉil veṇṇeyumuṇ</l>
<l>paṭṭikkaṉ ṟēkoṭṭāy cappāṇi paṟpanā pākoṭṭāy cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O calf of the cattle stall who, having come,</l>
<l>bringing [and] pressing mud and dust on [my] waist,</l>
<l>[and] having entered inside unseen,</l>
<l>ate the curds from the earthen vessel and the butter in the pot,</l>
<l>clap cappāṇi! O you with the lotus navel, clap cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
